snippet.title: Dash DE Lei-Lei [ダッシュＤＥレイレイ] Game Sample - PC/Doujin
snippet.description:
Original Air Date: November 23, 2008 (Revised Today!)

This is Dash DE Lei-Lei (or Dash DE Lei Lei), a game produced by EasyGameStation. It stars Lei-Lei (some know her as Hsien-Ko from Night Warriors/Darkstalkers) in a simple, yet relatively enjoyable game. The game features a few recurring characters like Felicia, Huitzil, Q-Bee and Anakaris as you run across the stages in the alloted time. There are five stages broken up into three segments and a bonus segment for a total of twenty dashes. The game has a few minor unlockables upon completion. Enjoy.
